name: ac_villager_reference
description: A bot for looking up information about villagers in Animal Crossing: New Horizons. Contains commands for looking up info about 1 or more villagers' birthdays, catchphrases, species, and personality types. You can also request an image of one villager, or a villagers bio (includes all info and picture). Made with help from acnhapi.com.
author: Michael Gillett
